Using meta tags in your web pages offers several benefits:

Search Visibility: Improve search engine rankings.
Click-Through Rates: Attract more clicks with compelling descriptions.
User Experience: Help users find and understand your content.
Social Sharing: Control how your content appears on social media.
Structured Data: Enhance search results with structured information.
Customization: Control how your page displays in search results.
Accessibility: Contribute to web accessibility with alt text and language info.
